title: Cinch Men's White Label Relaxed Fit Jean
description: Take-it-easy, relaxed fit waist, hip, thigh, and knee

White label is cinch's most popular fit for the guy who lives his life in denim. With a relaxed waist and hip in a mid-rise, cinch has created a stylish jean with all day comfort. Cinch jeans are hand-crafted for comfort and durability. Copper oxide cinch embossed rivets, non-ratcheting zipper slider, and double stitched reinforced felled seam on the inside of the legs to eliminate chafing. Finishing the look is a relaxed thigh and knee with a straight leg. White label has an 18 leg opening. The five-pocket, 100 percent cotton denim is pre-shrunk and fits as good tomorrow as it does today
